/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()

# CORS for /api/leads is set per-request by the Pages Function
# (lib/lead.js -> corsHeadersFor): same-origin by default, widened only via
# the ALLOWED_ORIGINS env var. We intentionally do NOT set a blanket
# Access-Control-Allow-Origin: * here - that would let any third-party site
# script submissions against the public lead endpoint and would override the
# per-request lockdown above it.
